Ok Cobalt is real<BR>
Greaves and vambraces drop in Old Sebilis<BR>
Gloves and the less-common boots drop in Karnors<BR>
The items all drop random off the mobs <BR>
<BR>
<BR>
Ok, this has probably already been answered but i don't have enough time to read all the posts (at school).  The greves of ALL Kunark class specific drop off of Venril Sathir in Karnor's Castle, so no the Greves do not drop in Old Sebilis.  And when I first went to these new dungeons, I was very surprised by all the items that dropped off of specific mobs, as opposed to what i hear.<BR>
